These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-1::.
There 2 different types of food: grapes, raspberry
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
1. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating raspberry and the person drinking lemonade have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |
| Food    | raspberry | grapes  |
| Sport   | lemonade    | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, mystery
1. the person drinking 7up and the person watching thriller movies have the same parity positions##9
2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | milk      | 7up       |
| Food       | mystery | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, r&b
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, brazilian
1. the fan folk and the indian have different parity positions##9
2. the brazilian is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | r&b     | folk       |
| Sport         | indian | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, mexican
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: pop, salsa
1. the fan salsa is on the left or right of the fan pop##3
2. the mexican and the fan salsa have different parity positions##9
3. the argentine is on the right of the fan pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican | argentine |
| Sport         | pop | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-5::.
