2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Beverage   | sprite      | iced-tea  |
| Hobby      | bird | goat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-6::.
